                     <interp inst="t18381126-19-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18381126-cd-17" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18381126-19-offence-1 t18381126-cd-17"></join>8th of November</rs>, ¾ b. weight of copper, value 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 1/2 oz. weight of brass, value 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. the goods of <persName id="t18381126-name-177" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-177" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-177" type="surname" value="PONTIFEX"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-177" type="given" value="EDMUND"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-177" type="occupation" value="copper-smiths"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18381126-19-offence-1 t18381126-name-177"></join>Edmund Pontifex</persName> and others, his masters.</rs>
