                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-179" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS RAWLER</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> He has worked there two years, but I had suspicion of him before—he had 18<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. a week at first, but since then 22<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. or 23<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. a week—he has a wife and one child.</p>
